article= <d> <p> <s>  By one vote, a defector from its own ranks, Premier Romano Prodi's  center-left coalition, Italy's second-longest serving government since  World War II, lost a confidence vote Friday in the Chamber of Deputies. </s> <s>   Prodi immediately offered his resignation to President Oscar Luigi  Scalfaro, who asked him to stay on as caretaker premier while the  head of state decides whether to call early elections or ask someone  else to be premier. </s> </p> </d>	abstract= <d> <p> <s> Prodi caretaker until president calls early elections or names another PM. </s> </p> </d>